<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="b22Nov1938"><font color="red">22 November 1938</font> <i>NLFF</i> (from Richard de la Mere to Paul L&eacute;on): Thank you for your letter of 20th November with which you sent me Mr Joyce&apos;s revised copy for the last four pages of Part 4 &hellip; you shall have back the four original pages just as soon as I get them back myself.  </div>
